data.description: This 4BR/2.5BA two-story craftsman style home is just what you have been looking for!  The thoughtful landscaping and covered front porch give it great curb appeal.  Walk in to the two story foyer with beautiful wood floors, dining room with coffered ceiling on the right, and open concept kitchen and living room.  Don't miss the dual pantries, one outfitted with an Elfa storage system, and the butler's pantry/desk area! Upstairs there is an owner's suite with tray ceiling, large walk-in closet, dual vanities, and separate soaking tub and shower.  There are 3 additional bedrooms and a hall bathroom. NEW ROOF! Located in The Infield, a low HOA neighborhood, with sidewalks and streetlights.  Easy access to the best schools, shopping, and the Exchange Gwinnett.
